Package com.mailSender

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    createObject
    Creates an object that takes value of certain cells as attributes for each row
    createSubject
    Generates subject based from the information extracted from the Excel sheet
    extractEmail
    Returns a value from a certain cell in an excel sheet.
    Main
    This project is a terminal-based program for sending emails extracted from an excel sheet.
    sendMail
    Creates a session for sending the emails.
    setupUser
    Constructs the sender's credentials.
    validateEmail
    Validates email under conditions that there are 3-30 characters before the '@' domain and if it includes @ char itself.
